Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君 小鳩 沒有什麼東西忘記帶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的（兩人）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這樣赤手空拳去遠足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我去把包拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事啦


